name: Yoostar Entertainment Group, Inc.
overview:
Yoostar 2 Yoostar 2 is an interactive gaming application created by the Yoostar Entertainment Group, Inc. Launched on March 8, 2011, this second version of the original Yoostar is no now compatible with the latest Xbox and PlayStation platforms and readily syncs with leading social networking sites right from the console. Updates include a fresh list of scenes from all-time favorite Hollywood films and television series of various genres.

The Company Established in 2007, Yoostar Entertainment Group, Inc. is currently headquartered in New York, New York with an office located in Los Angeles, California. The company specializes in the production of interactive entertainment gaming systems and web-based social networking services.
